## Charge/Intercept ##

#showtooltip
/use [noform:1,combat]Intercept;[noform:1,nocombat]Battle Stance;[form:1,combat]Berserker Stance;Charge
/startattack


## Mocking Blow ##

#showtooltip Mocking Blow
/cast [stance:1]Mocking Blow;[stance:2]Battle Stance;[stance:3]Battle Stance
/startattack


## Mortal Strike ##

#showtooltip Mortal Strike
/cleartarget [dead]
/targetenemy [noharm]
/startattack
/cast Mortal Strike


## Thunderclap ##

#showtooltip Thunder Clap
/cleartarget [dead]
/targetenemy [noharm]
/startattack
/cast Thunder Clap


## Rend ##

#showtooltip Rend
/cleartarget [dead]
/targetenemy [noharm]
/startattack
/cast Rend


## Overpower ##

#showtooltip Overpower
/cleartarget [dead][noharm]
/targetenemy [dead][noharm]
/startattack
/cast Overpower


## Overpower ## (This will switch your stance before casting)

#showtooltip Overpower
/cleartarget [dead]
/targetenemy [noharm]
/startattack
/cast Battle Stance
/cast Overpower


## Retaliation ##

#showtooltip Retaliation
/startattack
/cast Battle Stance
/cast Retaliation


## Sunder Armor ##

#showtooltip Sunder Armor
/cleartarget [dead]
/targetenemy [noharm]
/cancelaura Greater Blessing of Salvation
/cancelaura Blessing of Salvation
/cast Sunder Armor
/startattack
